        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-11-27T19:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-07-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="298" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d298">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The only record of the substance of this meeting that has been found is a summary
                    of conversation between <persName corresp="#p_SERJ1">Stettinius</persName> and
                        <persName corresp="#p_CWS1">Churchill</persName> in <persName corresp="#p_SERJ1">Stettinius</persName>, <ref target="#pg_60">pp.
                        60</ref>–<ref target="#pg_62">62</ref>. The meeting was “a large formal
                    dinner at Government House” given by the Governor and Commander in Chief of
                    Malta, Lieutenant General <persName corresp="#p_S3">Schreiber</persName>, in
                    honor of the American and British Delegations. The information given here with
                    respect to the meeting and the participants is taken from <persName corresp="#p_SERJ1">Stettinius</persName>, <ref target="#pg_56">pp. 56</ref>,
                        <ref target="#pg_60">60</ref>, <ref target="#pg_62">62</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
